      "content": "Add message ID tooltip to message rows in the S-Deck dashboard.\n\n**Work inside:** `.synapse/worktrees/developer-25-hover-message-id`\nCommit your changes to that branch. Do not push.\n\n**What to do:**\nIn `public/app.js`, find the message row HTML template in `renderMessages()`. The outermost message div currently looks like:\n```js\n<div id=\"msg-${m.id}\" class=\"message-row ${cls}\">\n```\n\nAdd a `title` attribute so hovering shows the message ID:\n```js\n<div id=\"msg-${m.id}\" class=\"message-row ${cls}\" title=\"msg #${m.id}\">\n```\n\nThat's the only change needed. `npm run build` must pass (it's a frontend-only change so build may be a no-op, but verify). Commit. Report DONE to cec50b17:0.",
